item.description: I am currently a Master student in Computer Science at University of California, Los Angeles. Before moving to my graduate study, I receivced my Bachelor Degree in Computing at Macao Polytechnic Institute. I am broadly interested in many topics related to Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence. My recent works are mostly related to Generative Models and Reinforcement Learning.
